# Layout (`src/app/layout` + `core/layout`)

## Structure

- `AppShellComponent` — grid: sidebar column + `app-shell__main` (topbar + scrollable `router-outlet` content).
- `SidebarComponent` — brand row (BHCOM + portal suffix from `PORTAL_CONFIG`), collapsible nav (desktop), drawer (mobile).
- Nav types: `layout/sidebar/nav.model.ts`; configs: `employee-nav.config.ts`, `admin-nav.config.ts`.
- `PORTAL_CONFIG` provided on shell route in `employee.routes.ts` / `admin.routes.ts` (sidebar injects nav + `shell.brandSuffixKey`).
- `TopbarComponent` — hamburger (mobile only), theme/notifications/profile actions.
- `LanguagePickerComponent` (`layout/language-picker/`) — globe language menu; shared by topbar and login page.
- `ThemePickerComponent` (`layout/theme-picker/`) — light/dark theme menu; shared by topbar and login page.
- Profile icon opens **account menu** (`topbar.account.*`): Profile/Settings close menu only; **Log out** calls `AuthService.logout()` then navigates to `PORTAL_CONFIG.loginUrl` (`/login` or `/admin/login`).

## SidebarService (`core/layout/sidebar.service.ts`)

| API | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `collapsed` / `toggle()` / `setCollapsed()` | Desktop narrow sidebar (persisted `localStorage`) |
| `mobileOpen` / `openMobile()` / `closeMobile()` | Mobile drawer (not persisted) |

On `openMobile()`: `document.body` overflow hidden. On `NavigationEnd`: `closeMobile()`.

## Mobile drawer (≤768px)

- Topbar: `LucideMenu` → `openMobile()`.
- Sidebar: `position: fixed`, slides in; brand row shows **X** (`closeMobile`), not panel collapse toggle.
- `app-shell`: backdrop button when `mobileOpen()`; single-column grid.
- i18n: `topbar.openMenu`, `sidebar.close`, `sidebar.collapse` / `sidebar.expand`.

## Desktop sidebar

- Viewport height (`100vh`), nav area scrolls (`overflow-y` on `.sidebar__nav`).
- Brand row: `PanelLeftClose` / `PanelLeftOpen` for collapse.

## Styling

- Use `@use 'styles/breakpoints' as *` + `@include below-md` in layout SCSS.
- Content padding: CSS vars from `styles.scss` (`--layout-padding-x-mobile`, etc.).
- **Portal accent:** `AppShellComponent` host class `portal-employee` | `portal-admin` (from `PORTAL_CONFIG`); tokens in `src/styles/_portal-accent.scss` (`--portal-accent`, `--portal-accent-muted`, `--portal-accent-nav-bg`). Login uses `.login--employee` / `.login--admin` on the same tokens. Active sidebar link: inset 3px border + tinted background; brand portal suffix uses muted accent.
